1
00:00:30,850 --> 00:00:33,290
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:36,230
[Episode 21 Know My Own]

3
00:01:12,390 --> 00:01:13,990
What are you thinking about?

4
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,890
It's none of your business.

5
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,110
You and I, right now,

6
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:20,440
are each responsible
for the county yamen and Xiqianhua,

7
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:22,640
bearing responsibility for the safety
of the entire Yin-Yang Crossing.

8
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,670
Of course I will check on you,

9
00:01:23,670 --> 00:01:24,210
alright?

10
00:01:25,670 --> 00:01:27,130
Such a bureaucratic tone.

11
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,580
People would think

12
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:30,230
you got possessed by Lord Bai.

13
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:31,280
I'm warning you.

14
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,720
You can insult me all you like,

15
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:34,580
but you can't slander my Lord Bai.

16
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:35,680
What's wrong?

17
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,210
Who's slandering him?

18
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,770
I'm just telling the truth.

19
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:40,830
Bell Spirit,

20
00:01:41,030 --> 00:01:42,590
I was kind enough to check in on you.

21
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:44,100
What's with your attitude?

22
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,800
Even if you wanted
to be possessed by Lady Fufeng,

23
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,240
you wouldn't even be qualified, okay?

24
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,190
I don't need it.

25
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,000
As long as my Lady

26
00:01:50,130 --> 00:01:52,259
is doing well herself, that's enough.

27
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,330
What do you mean by that?

28
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:56,780
Are you implying
Lord Bai isn't doing well?

29
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:57,940
Yes, you're right.

30
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,600
Anyway, my lord is

31
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,400
not expected to recover.

32
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:08,350
Your lord can still be saved.

33
00:02:08,610 --> 00:02:09,610
He should be fine.

34
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:11,050
He...

35
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:13,820
Lord Bai can still be saved?

36
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:16,770
But my Lady is beyond saving.

37
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:20,210
Hold on.

38
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:21,650
What do you mean by that?

39
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:23,090
Make yourself clear!

40
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,190
What do I mean?

41
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,350
What does it have to do with you anyway?

42
00:02:27,350 --> 00:02:29,280
What could you possibly do to help?

43
00:02:30,350 --> 00:02:31,120
So annoying.

44
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,040
Is this

45
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,860
what death feels like?

46
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,440
My Lady.

47
00:03:29,410 --> 00:03:30,840
My Lady, why...

48
00:03:32,610 --> 00:03:33,070
My Lady.

49
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:35,310
Why are you also...

50
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,090
That was quite a grand bow.

51
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,400
Did you think I was dead too?

52
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,579
Feel it fully, your life,

53
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,240
your heartbeat,

54
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,329
and your pain.

55
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:07,600
Liu Fufeng,

56
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,960
how could you treat this like a game?

57
00:04:10,510 --> 00:04:12,160
How am I treating it like a game?

58
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,960
You waited 100 years for this heart

59
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,230
and spent 100 years planning for it!

60
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:18,160
How... how could you give it away again?

61
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,100
It's my thing,

62
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:22,540
so I get to decide what to do with it.

63
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,970
Then how are you?

64
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,680
Are you injured?

65
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,170
As long as you don't betray me,

66
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:33,360
I will suffer no harm.

67
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:42,510
In the past,

68
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:45,240
that half a heart

69
00:04:45,659 --> 00:04:47,030
was in a dormant state.

70
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,680
But now,

71
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:50,950
the one I lent to you

72
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:53,440
has been completely awakened.

73
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,440
Therefore,

74
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:57,270
you are unable to control

75
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,560
this surging spiritual power.

76
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,240
Now,

77
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,150
you and I

78
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,040
are spiritually connected—

79
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:09,560
just like the
spiritual power in the world,

80
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,620
it can flow and circulate between us.

81
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:17,010
My Lady.

82
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,560
I, Bai Shanjun, hereby swear

83
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:23,350
that in this lifetime, with this heart,

84
00:05:23,710 --> 00:05:25,040
I will never betray you.

85
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:29,660
Bai Shanjun.

86
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,000
This half a heart

87
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,159
is not only for you,

88
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,070
but also for Yin-Yang Crossing.

89
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,680
My Lady.

90
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,920
I will definitely learn to master it,

91
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:47,300
and use it to help you, protect you,

92
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:50,110
and protect this Yin-Yang Crossing.

93
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,500
This is the path I chose

94
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,830
and the responsibility I must bear.

95
00:05:55,659 --> 00:05:56,950
Big words,

96
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,480
but you see—

97
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,040
those words came from a helper

98
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,010
who can barely walk.

99
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:08,710
Please, My Lady,

100
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,500
teach me how to control it.

101
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,660
Do not force it.

102
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,810
Go with the flow.

103
00:06:52,110 --> 00:06:53,550
What you have now

104
00:06:53,930 --> 00:06:56,110
is a treasure that can drive
every demon and spirit

105
00:06:56,110 --> 00:06:57,840
within 100 miles into a frenzy.

106
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,110
If you can't learn to live with it,

107
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,390
then they'll come for it,

108
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,950
tear you apart,

109
00:07:05,370 --> 00:07:06,970
and claim it for themselves.

110
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:19,930
Control it,

111
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:20,990
maseter it,

112
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:23,050
and do not let it control you.

113
00:07:50,490 --> 00:07:52,880
Are you angry, My Lady?

114
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,510
This half a heart
allows me to feel your...

115
00:07:58,470 --> 00:07:59,800
Focus on your training.

116
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,040
My Lady,

117
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,360
I can truly feel

118
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,480
your emotions now.

119
00:08:08,730 --> 00:08:11,200
And you can feel mine as well.

120
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:16,550
The smug look on your face when you

121
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:18,090
deliberately threw yourself at me

122
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:19,380
told me everything

123
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,240
that I needed to know.

124
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:23,490
My Lady,

125
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:25,440
I'm a beginner with spiritual power.

126
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,440
I... I haven't mastered it yet.

127
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,770
My Lady,

128
00:08:30,790 --> 00:08:32,650
you're not going to hit me, right?

129
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,890
Don't forget I can feel your emotions.

130
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:39,400
Since you're learning so fast,

131
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:42,400
you don't need to practice tomorrow.

132
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:48,150
[Dedication Above Self]

133
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:03,740
Deputy Magistrate Shi,

134
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,720
I think this compensation document

135
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,580
still needs a few more revisions.

136
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,120
My Lord!

137
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,000
Xiaohu, I'm back.

138
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:33,480
You're alive!

139
00:09:34,070 --> 00:09:34,950
I can touch you!

140
00:09:35,010 --> 00:09:36,270
And you're still warm!

141
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,560
Didn't you...

142
00:09:38,730 --> 00:09:40,200
People over at spiritual pool said...

143
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,240
I thought you...

144
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,120
You scared the life out of me!

145
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:46,960
You have no idea

146
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,080
that I haven't slept for days,

147
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,730
spending all day thinking about
how to write your heroic achievements.

148
00:09:50,730 --> 00:09:52,850
Then show me what you wrote.

149
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,550
Did you include

150
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:55,630
my heroic figure?

151
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,790
You're still in the mood to joke?

152
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,520
It's better that you're alive.

153
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:07,550
You have no idea how hard it was for me

154
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,150
to make all of this up for you.

155
00:10:09,290 --> 00:10:10,170
Let me see.

156
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:22,720
My Lord.

157
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,140
was it because Lady Fufeng...

158
00:10:27,610 --> 00:10:28,650
Yes, she saved me.

159
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,120
From now on,

160
00:10:31,690 --> 00:10:33,620
I will protect this place with her.

161
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,080
Alright.

162
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:53,590
By order of Lady Fufeng:

163
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:55,550
Qian Wanqian,

164
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,470
though you are not the primary culprit,

165
00:10:57,470 --> 00:11:00,550
you helped a villain commit evil deeds,
and your sins are grave.

166
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:03,260
For all those whose families were ruined
by the Fortune-Turning Master,

167
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:06,200
you must use all your wealth to
compensate them double for their losses

168
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,130
and provide the care they deserve.

169
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,230
Yes, yes.

170
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:14,730
I will definitely do it.

171
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:18,550
I will do more good deeds
for the people of Yin-Yang Crossing,

172
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,950
and use the rest of my life

173
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,600
to make amends for my mistakes.

174
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,390
In addition,

175
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:25,120
you must serve ten years
in the county jail.

176
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,390
This is the punishment you deserve.

177
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,160
My Lady.

178
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,120
I plead guilty.

179
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,430
But my son, Jinlang—

180
00:11:32,430 --> 00:11:34,670
he was deeply corrupted by the evil power.

181
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:37,240
His mind is now like that of a child,

182
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,810
and he can no longer take care of himself.

183
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:42,550
Come in.

184
00:11:59,850 --> 00:12:02,000
He was transformed
from the thumb ring you wore,

185
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,260
and he has a pure heart.

186
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:05,670
He played a big role in exposing

187
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:06,910
Bai Han's conspiracy.

188
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:08,120
If you don't mind,

189
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,050
you can be his adoptive father.

190
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:13,680
Let him inherit your family business
and look after Jinlang for you.

191
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,540
What do you say?

192
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,390
Child,

193
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,450
are you truly willing to

194
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:20,270
take care of Jinlang for me?

195
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:26,600
Father, I am.

196
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:33,120
It's just that I don't have a name yet.

197
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:37,320
Gold and jade

198
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:40,350
are nothing but worldly possessions.

199
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,650
They are passing clouds

200
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,690
and also shackles.

201
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,630
As a father, I take full blame

202
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,750
for letting them blind my eyes,

203
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:54,550
which ultimately harmed my own son.

204
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,430
In that case,

205
00:12:57,430 --> 00:12:58,430
from now on,

206
00:12:59,130 --> 00:13:00,530
you'll be named Shulang.

207
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,450
Study, learn characters,

208
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:03,780
learn right from wrong,

209
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:07,040
and understand the wisdom of
the past and present.

210
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,750
I truly hope

211
00:13:10,570 --> 00:13:12,220
you can be like Lady Fufeng

212
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,430
or the county magistrate Bai,

213
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:17,240
and bring genuine,

214
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,910
concrete benefits

215
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,160
to Yin-Yang Crossing.

216
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,440
Thank you for giving me my name, Father.

217
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,000
Master.

218
00:14:10,430 --> 00:14:11,760
Judging by these marks,

219
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,780
the rock veins cracked naturally,

220
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:15,430
allowing the evil power to seep out.

221
00:14:15,430 --> 00:14:18,120
It must be a new leak caused
by the circulation of ground vapor.

222
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:21,120
There are no signs
of sabotage or arrays nearby.

223
00:14:28,130 --> 00:14:29,630
It seems we were overthinking things.

224
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,370
Bai Han's spiritual consciousness
in the mine that day

225
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:33,260
was purified by you and Bai Shanjun,

226
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:34,860
then scattered to the winds.

227
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:37,470
This time, it's likely just an accident.

228
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,150
Fengling,

229
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,240
don't you think

230
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:43,940
it went a bit too smoothly this time?

231
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:51,570
I hope I'm just overthinking things.

232
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,800
The seepage of evil power here is weak,

233
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:56,550
yet it's enough to disrupt people's minds.

234
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,120
Since it was found here,

235
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,240
we cannot just ignore it.

236
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:03,060
Follow the trail
of the dissipating evil power

237
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:04,920
and check on the nearby villages.

238
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:11,960
Master.

239
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:14,670
I have one more thing to say.

240
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:18,360
You gave your fully awakened tree heart

241
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:19,550
to Bai Shanjun this time.

242
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:21,270
A connection like that
is no trivial matter.

243
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,080
What if...

244
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,120
Fengling.

245
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,740
I know what you are worried about.

246
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,840
I've guarded the Yin-Yang Crossing

247
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,530
for thousands of years.

248
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,520
Sometimes I just feel so tired.

249
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:41,230
I'm so tired that,

250
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:45,120
watching the water level
of the spiritual pool drop day by day,

251
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,380
I find myself thinking

252
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:49,010
that just fading into sleep right here

253
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:51,410
might not be a bad thing after all.

254
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,330
Regarding Bai Shanjun,

255
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,550
we have both witnessed

256
00:15:57,430 --> 00:15:59,790
everything he went through on his journey.

257
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:00,750
He is stubborn,

258
00:16:01,430 --> 00:16:03,430
and sometimes ridiculously naive.

259
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:10,250
But he holds firm to his principles
and sees a clear path ahead.

260
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:11,840
This time,

261
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:15,240
I'm the one who forced
this heavy burden on him.

262
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,200
Fengling.

263
00:16:22,430 --> 00:16:23,430
I believe in him.

264
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,630
Yes, My Lady.

265
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,000
I understand.

266
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:36,080
Deputy Magistrate Shi,

267
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:39,230
don't you think this is
a bit too coincidental?

268
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:42,380
Every time a great disaster
occurs in the mortal realm,

269
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:44,240
the cracks in the
Yin-Yang Crossing's earth veins

270
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,750
either increasing or worsening.

271
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:46,790
or worsening.

272
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:57,360
What's wrong, My Lord?

273
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,290
What happened?

274
00:16:58,530 --> 00:16:59,660
It's the evil power.

275
00:17:02,530 --> 00:17:03,110
Master.

276
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,119
Go down the mountain immediately

277
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,319
and check on the town.

278
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:07,630
I'll go check on the seal.

279
00:17:07,630 --> 00:17:08,430
Yes, My Lady.

280
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:18,359
My Lord!

281
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:20,290
Something terrible has happened!

282
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,359
The marketplace outside is in chaos.

283
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:24,490
People seem to be possessed by demons—

284
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,680
they are smashing, looting, and burning.

285
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,190
The situation is out of control!

286
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:28,190
And what's worse,

287
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:29,800
many people have already

288
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:31,930
gathered outside Xiqianhua Mansion.

289
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:34,470
Hurry up and take some men

290
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:35,820
to the marketplace to maintain order.

291
00:17:35,820 --> 00:17:36,800
Do your best to calm them down,

292
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:37,840
and use every possible means

293
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,200
to suppress the panic.

294
00:17:39,220 --> 00:17:40,190
Yes, My Lord!

295
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:40,670
Yes.

296
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,690
Fufeng, where are you?

297
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:15,340
My Lady.

298
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:20,440
What... what is this?

299
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:23,740
Look over there.

300
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:32,040
Feel it

301
00:18:32,470 --> 00:18:33,560
with your heart.

302
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,700
They're coming from the outside,

303
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:04,230
drifting in from the crowd in the town—

304
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:06,710
just like what I felt at the marketplace.

305
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:09,470
So, it's the panic in people's hearts

306
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,840
that breeds the evil power.

307
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:11,950
And the evil power

308
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,900
is being drawn straight here.

309
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:18,800
I have guarded this place for 1,000 years—

310
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:19,600
sealing,

311
00:19:19,620 --> 00:19:20,420
reinforcing,

312
00:19:20,650 --> 00:19:21,510
and purifying,

313
00:19:21,930 --> 00:19:23,080
over and over again.

314
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:26,790
I always thought this crack
was the source of all evil,

315
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,520
constantly seeping out malice

316
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:30,630
and polluting the mortal realm.

317
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:32,560
Little did I know,

318
00:19:33,190 --> 00:19:35,990
the cause and effect might be
the other way around.

319
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,350
People suffer pain first,

320
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,210
which then breeds the evil power,

321
00:19:40,210 --> 00:19:42,470
allowing Bai Han to take advantage of it.

322
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:43,800
Yes.

323
00:19:44,870 --> 00:19:47,330
The mortal realm
bred fear and malice first,

324
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:49,470
which then sank here,

325
00:19:49,670 --> 00:19:51,070
breeding the evil power.

326
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:52,880
And this spring

327
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:55,690
is a wound constantly being
torn open by the evil power—

328
00:19:55,690 --> 00:19:57,250
one that can never heal.

329
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:00,760
So whenever there's famine or war,

330
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:03,560
the seal here grows especially strained.

331
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:05,990
It isn't because something
stirs beneath the earth—

332
00:20:05,990 --> 00:20:08,390
it's because the people's hearts are sick.

333
00:20:10,570 --> 00:20:12,500
I've been foolish for 1,000 years.

334
00:20:12,910 --> 00:20:15,480
Bai Han's plague of lies is the only thing

335
00:20:16,130 --> 00:20:18,190
that made me see everything clearly.

336
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:20,480
Liu Fufeng is an evil demon!

337
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,230
She will be punished by Heaven!

338
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:24,540
Yin-Yang Crossing is doomed!

339
00:20:24,650 --> 00:20:26,130
We are all going to die!

340
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:36,430
Whispers echo in the forest,
each cry like weeping.

341
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:40,710
Mimicking human speech,
it drains away vitality.

342
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:45,590
Old things return,
shifting within the heart.

343
00:20:45,610 --> 00:20:47,940
Not their rightful owner—

344
00:20:47,970 --> 00:20:50,770
calamity will not cease.

345
00:21:06,530 --> 00:21:07,750
What Shuan said is true.

346
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,760
That demon woman stole someone's heart,

347
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:09,850
and brought this disaster upon us!

348
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:10,600
All these years,

349
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,880
we've been fooled by Xiqianhua

350
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,430
and that damn Lady Fufeng!

351
00:21:13,430 --> 00:21:13,990
How dare they!

352
00:21:13,990 --> 00:21:14,840
Give me back my mother's life!

353
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:15,800
Give me back my father's life!

354
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:16,800
Let them smash it.

355
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:18,470
Look at their eyes.

356
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:20,710
That's just fear turning into violence.

357
00:21:20,710 --> 00:21:21,840
They won't listen

358
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:24,250
to reason right now.

359
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:25,280
Take it out!

360
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,190
Smash it!

361
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:28,220
Smash it!

362
00:21:28,250 --> 00:21:28,920
Pelt it!

363
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:29,470
Smash it!

364
00:21:29,470 --> 00:21:30,280
Harder!

365
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,190
Smash it!

366
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:33,270
Smash it!

367
00:21:35,990 --> 00:21:36,650
Destroy it!

368
00:21:43,120 --> 00:21:44,670
I underestimated Bai Han

369
00:21:44,990 --> 00:21:46,050
and the evil power.

370
00:21:46,610 --> 00:21:48,460
As for the matter
of the Fortune-Turning Master,

371
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:49,990
it was my own lack of foresight

372
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:52,470
that eventually brought this disaster
upon the people.

373
00:21:52,470 --> 00:21:54,130
The people's minds are vulnerable.

374
00:21:54,130 --> 00:21:55,840
And now they're manipulated
by the evil power—

375
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:57,370
they are miserable as well.

376
00:21:58,950 --> 00:21:59,950
But what does this

377
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,630
have anything to do with you?

378
00:22:32,950 --> 00:22:33,560
Are you okay?

379
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:34,190
Look, everyone!

380
00:22:34,190 --> 00:22:35,490
Isn't that Liu Fufeng?

381
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:36,910
I saw her!

382
00:22:36,910 --> 00:22:38,910
She was trying to kill that child!

383
00:22:38,910 --> 00:22:39,290
Hurry!

384
00:22:39,290 --> 00:22:41,620
Catch her! Catch her!

385
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,840
Hurry, catch her!

386
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:45,970
Catch her!

387
00:22:46,390 --> 00:22:47,080
Pelt her!

388
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:48,470
Pelt her to death!

389
00:22:48,470 --> 00:22:49,150
Pelt her!

390
00:22:49,150 --> 00:22:50,230
Pelt her to death!

391
00:22:50,390 --> 00:22:51,470
Pelt her to death!

392
00:22:51,490 --> 00:22:52,580
Pelt her to death!

393
00:23:02,090 --> 00:23:03,050
You monster!

394
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:05,150
Pelt her!

395
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:06,040
Liar!

396
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:09,080
Have you all

397
00:23:11,020 --> 00:23:11,970
truly forgotten

398
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,230
that Lady Fufeng
has protected you all these years?

399
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:15,600
How could you believe those rumors

400
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,060
and treat her like a demon?

401
00:23:17,190 --> 00:23:19,190
It's that corrupt official, Bai Shanjun!

402
00:23:19,190 --> 00:23:20,880
He's no good either!

403
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,300
Catch him! Burn him!

404
00:23:22,320 --> 00:23:23,450
Burn him!

405
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:30,000
Burn him to death!

406
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:18,710
All this hatred

407
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:20,950
was meant for me.

408
00:24:22,220 --> 00:24:23,050
I told you

409
00:24:23,710 --> 00:24:26,600
that I will always stand up for you.

410
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:35,840
Are you okay?

411
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:40,820
How touching.

412
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,940
My dear Fufeng,

413
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:46,090
and this devoted young magistrate.

414
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:49,190
Are you two still this naive?

415
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:50,840
Human hearts

416
00:24:51,430 --> 00:24:53,910
are never worth protecting.

417
00:24:54,190 --> 00:24:55,600
Bai Han, show yourself!

418
00:24:55,620 --> 00:24:57,560
Hiding in the shadows
is the behavior of a coward.

419
00:24:57,560 --> 00:25:00,210
I am everywhere, Magistrate.

420
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:02,910
Once people's minds start to crack,

421
00:25:02,930 --> 00:25:04,520
there's no stopping the flood.

422
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:05,320
Look,

423
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:07,360
their fear and curses are

424
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:09,670
becoming a source of power for me.

425
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:11,530
It's wonderful.

426
00:25:11,730 --> 00:25:12,960
What do you want?

427
00:25:13,290 --> 00:25:15,080
Hand over the complete tree heart,

428
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:16,560
your body,

429
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:19,880
and your authority over Yin-Yang Crossing.

430
00:25:20,950 --> 00:25:22,710
If I give you the tree heart,

431
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:24,650
will you stop all this

432
00:25:24,950 --> 00:25:26,880
and restore everything to normal?

433
00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:28,020
Fufeng!

434
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:28,880
Of course.

435
00:25:29,390 --> 00:25:31,670
If I can manipulate them to feel fear,

436
00:25:31,810 --> 00:25:33,820
I can also take that fear away.

437
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:36,080
Everything will be back
on the right track.

438
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:39,610
Isn't this what you've wished for
over the past thousand years?

439
00:25:41,190 --> 00:25:41,820
Fufeng,

440
00:25:42,210 --> 00:25:44,190
I know you care about
the people of Yin-Yang Crossing.

441
00:25:44,190 --> 00:25:45,990
But you mustn't hand over
your authority to him.

442
00:25:45,990 --> 00:25:47,390
Once you lose the power
to keep him in check,

443
00:25:47,390 --> 00:25:48,230
and lose your spiritual power,

444
00:25:48,230 --> 00:25:49,950
he will immediately tear off his disguise

445
00:25:49,950 --> 00:25:52,080
and turn this place into a living hell.

446
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:54,150
Oh, Fufeng.

447
00:25:54,930 --> 00:25:56,440
He is just a mortal.

448
00:25:56,470 --> 00:25:58,320
His lifespan won't reach a hundred years.

449
00:25:58,320 --> 00:26:00,320
What could he possibly understand?

450
00:26:00,320 --> 00:26:01,980
Look at those people outside.

451
00:26:02,150 --> 00:26:03,560
A few lines of rumors are all it takes

452
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:05,190
for them to throw filth at you,

453
00:26:05,190 --> 00:26:06,760
and cast stones at you.

454
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:09,150
Has everything you've done for 1,000 years

455
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:10,990
really meant anything at all?

456
00:26:11,470 --> 00:26:13,600
Fufeng, don't listen to his nonsense.

457
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:14,600
Every person you saved,

458
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,950
every night you guarded,

459
00:26:15,950 --> 00:26:16,950
and every hope you gave,

460
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:17,990
they all mean something.

461
00:26:17,990 --> 00:26:19,470
The human heart is not made of stone.

462
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:21,080
Malice may be stirred up and provoked,

463
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,710
but kindness has never truly disappeared.

464
00:26:22,710 --> 00:26:23,990
What we need to do isn't to forget,

465
00:26:23,990 --> 00:26:25,190
but to ignite it.

466
00:26:40,260 --> 00:26:41,020
Bai Han.

467
00:26:41,430 --> 00:26:42,710
Your incitement

468
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:45,710
will shake the stability
of Yin-Yang Crossing from its core.

469
00:26:45,710 --> 00:26:46,670
But it will also inevitably expose

470
00:26:46,670 --> 00:26:49,070
the long-hidden source of your evil power.

471
00:26:49,270 --> 00:26:51,130
Taking such a desperate measure,

472
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:53,100
it seems your days are numbered.

473
00:26:55,650 --> 00:26:57,300
Stubborn!

474
00:27:16,100 --> 00:27:16,700
Look,

475
00:27:17,290 --> 00:27:19,150
it's not all-powerful after all.

476
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,480
Enough talking.
